flowRoot.flowPara: This is the text that introduces what ASME is all about, what we do, and the kinds of activities and stuff we have. It basically explains why we're so awesome, and why you should get involved with us and stuff.
Here we explain what you can do to get involved. You can get involved with a project, have a leadership position, or just kind of come to events and get some free pizza. Whatever you want to do.
